t Stripe.\" The system does nothing of the sort \u2014 the older 30-day rule on individual commission rows is what actually cancels the money. Either build the job, or change the dashboard to tell the truth.\n    - **Source:** Commit-batch review item #3 (commit `85f2673`).\n",
